mysql_groundtruth: SELECT DISTINCT VIEWER_ID AS ID FROM VIEWS GROUP BY VIEW_DATE, VIEWER_ID HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT ARTICLE_ID) > 1 ORDER BY ID

SELECT DISTINCT V1.VIEWER_ID AS ID FROM VIEWS V1 JOIN VIEWS V2 ON (V1.VIEW_DATE = V2.VIEW_DATE OR (V1.VIEW_DATE IS NULL AND V2.VIEW_DATE IS NULL)) AND V1.VIEWER_ID = V2.VIEWER_ID AND V1.ARTICLE_ID != V2.ARTICLE_ID ORDER BY 1
